{"tid":2137981,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【香港】政府近月發逾29萬份豁免強制檢疫","createTime":"2020-08-03T10:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T03:12:02.000Z","uid":259088,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"bf78e8436ea8b4860f59633bc0842ffb0cb9d07d","tid":2137981,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:08:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539729-20200724.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539729-20200724.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Surr%2FXenqJySG8qcND35%2F%2FDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=9f0a50f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539729-20200724.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e3e13a4b\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539729-20200724.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n根據《預防及控制疾病條例》，政府如信納某類別人士符合特定條件，可豁免他們抵港後強制檢疫14日，衞生署會發出醫學監察通知書。本台向衞生署查詢後，當局提供資料顯示，<strong>署方6月於各出入境管制站，發出45953份醫學監察通知書，較5月份多5733份，亦是自3月以來最多的月份。本月截至22日，則發出39584份通知書。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">保安局本月8日書面回覆立法會議員提問時透露，政府由2月至5月一共發出逾20萬份醫學監察通知書。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">換言之，由2月至前日，有超過29萬人次入境後毋須接受強制檢疫</span></span></strong>，但要接受14天醫學監察，期間須佩戴口罩和每天量度體溫兩次。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署指，要出入本港履行職責的機組人員，以及跨境貨車司機與必要的陪同人員，若持有14日內發出的有效醫學監察通知書，不會於每次入境時獲發新的通知書。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">現時有33類人士獲豁免檢疫</span></span>，包括跨境貨車司機、機組人員、船員、政府人員、為香港供應個人防護裝備相關人員、在內地從事生產作業的香港企業的人員、在內地提供專業服務的建造業人員、在內地進行物流活動人員等等。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>本台向衞生署查詢分類數字，以了解過去數月獲豁免檢疫人士中，有多少屬於船員、機組人員或其他類別。<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">衞生署回應時指，沒有備存分項數字。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇下港共豁免左邊32類人士免受強制檢疫<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2097830\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2097830</a>"},{"pid":"358913d2dcb4a8e05d642f36a7d1ac99bee4aa3b","tid":2137981,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5253e265b4816f431ead02bd975dcc4c1d9adf5d","tid":2137981,"uid":55955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:09:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41bc6eafa4b55a7f992564b4fcf36bf88b6ef8bb","tid":2137981,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:18:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c28252f7719af383b183fb89bde5022da23767","tid":2137981,"uid":200479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:40:51.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86895aa71a29bdcb181c90f17d75e683bad00f2","tid":2137981,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:46:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86ca996b347f309e14a8811ec74e107855aa1c6d","tid":2137981,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T10:48:45.000Z","msg":"齊心抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934bc979158791ba48f2360b04d3bd1f76ed1196","tid":2137981,"uid":259088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-04T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s